Creating the Database from Script 1

·          Download the Code from file

·           Go to SQL Server Management Studio.

·          To open the file, Double Click or Right Click ---- > Click Open, selecting the file that you downloaded from Code file in order to

open the file


·         Then the file will open in SQL server Management Studio (SSMS) like below.

 

 

  ·         Click execute above the Object explorer.

 

 Note: As these are 7 files it takes some time to load. Be Patience and wait till it loads.

 

  ·         Files loaded successfully, as shown below.

 

 

 ·         Right Click on Database --- > Click Refresh ---- > to view the Database that is created.

 


 ·         New Database with 7 tables is viewed below.
